<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Laura Bottino</author>
<hymn_number>4699</hymn_number>
<title>You</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 When I'm alone on this road
 And there's no one around me
 You, You
 In the darkness of the night
 When my fears overcome me
 You, You

[V2]
 Troubles take away my joy
 But you come and give me breaths of life

[V3]
 In the secret of my heart
 I know who You are
 You, You
 When I cry out of despair
 Your hand heals all my hurts
 You, You

[V4]
 I've seen the glory of the Holy God
 Spend my time with Him is all I want
 Show me how your love
 Can change the hardest heart
 I want to live for You Lord unconditionally

[V5]
 Oh God, God Almighty
 God, God Almighty
 God, Name above all name

[V6]
 In the secret of my heart
 I know who You are
 You, You are God</lyrics>
</song>